arStrings.szText: Diablo® IV: Vessel of Hatred™ - Deluxe Edition

Uncover the next chapter of Diablo IV in Vessel of Hatred and continue your fight to thwart the diabolical lot of the Prime Evil, Mephisto. Purchase Vessel of Hatred to battle as the all-new Spiritborn class and Expand your map to the new region of Nahantu.
